name: Wire Beaded Dragonfly Earrings
description:
Hand twisted silver tone memory wire earrings in the shape of a dragonfly. The head of dragonfly is the color bead of your choice! Select a different color dragonfly if you choose. Other colors available: red, copper, gold, green, blue, purple, brown, black, pastel pink. 
Total earring measures 2 inches from earring hook to bottom of hand made charm. 
For those of you without pierced ears I can add clip on if specified in your order. 

Email me with any questions, if you would like to change the color combo of the wire or bead, or if you need the clip on style: 
 
sarasbeadedboutique@yahoo.com

Thanks for you interest in this product! Happy browsing/shopping!

name: Black Beauty Earrings
description:
Black colored memory wire hand twisted into scroll work design of an earring stem. Black faceted plastic bead dangles from earring stem. Four petal hand shaped black wire flower dangles from bead. Total earring measures 2 and 1/2 inches from top of earring hook to bottom of flower dangle. 

Let me know if you would like a different color combo! 
Colors available: red, copper, gold, green, silver, blue, purple, brown, pastel pink

Thanks for your interest!! Happy browsing/shopping!
